1. Clone the Repository
cmd:
git clone [https://github.com/sanheeth-singh/taskflow.git](https://github.com/sanheeth-singh/taskflow.git)
cd taskflow

2. Create a Virtual Environment
cmd:
# Windows
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate

# Mac/Linux
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

3. Install Dependencies
cmd:
pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Initialize Database
Since this project uses Flask-Migrate, run the upgrade command to generate the database schema:
cmd:
flask db upgrade

4. Initialize Database
